===石油及天然氣===
[[File:StatfjordA(Jarvin1982).jpg|thumb]]

早於1859年，在北海的沿岸地區已經發現了石油，而在1910年則發現了天然氣<ref name="Glennie">{{Cite book| last =Glennie | first = K. W.| year =1998| title = Petroleum Geology of the North Sea: Basic Concepts and Recent Advances | publisher =Blackwell Publishing | pages =11–12| url = http://books.google.com/?id=BRoJwOzO3NUC&pg=PA11|isbn=978-0-632-03845-9}}</ref>。自1966年，周邊的國家便開採石油及天然氣。

試鑽油井自1966年啟用，其後在1969年，{{link-en|菲利普斯石油公司|Phillips Petroleum Company}}發現Ekofisk油田，其中含有低硫的原油<ref name="Ekofisk">{{cite book
|last=Pratt
|first=J. A.
|editor=T. Priest, & Cas James
|title=Offshore Pioneers: Brown & Root and the History of Offshore Oil and Gas
|url= http://books.google.com/?id=TW6yMgPdgbQC&pg=PP1
|accessdate=2008-12-08
|year=1997
|publisher=Gulf Professional Publishing
|isbn=0-88415-138-7
|page=222
|chapter=Ekofisk and Early North Sea Oil
}}</ref><ref name="Lohne">{{cite book
|last= Lohne
|first=Øystein
|title=The Oil Industry and Government Strategy in the North Sea
|url=http://books.google.com/?id=jZIOAAAAQAAJ&pg=PA73
|year=1980
|publisher=Taylor & Francis
|isbn=0-918714-02-8
|page=74
|chapter=The Economic Attraction
}}
</ref>。1971年商業開發正式開始，以油輪運輸原油。1975年後，Ekofisk油田與英國的輸油管接通，到1977年輸油管伸延到德國<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = TOTAL E&P NORGE AS – The history of Fina Exploration 1965–2000
 |work        = About TOTAL E&P NORGE > History > Fina
